This project downloads and uses the `psiphon-tunnel-core` binary which is
licensed by Psiphon Inc. / Psiphon Labs under its own open-source license
(Eclipse Public License / Apache 2.0; see https://github.com/Psiphon-Labs/psiphon-tunnel-core).
This repository does NOT bundle that binary; it downloads it from its official
release channel at install time, subject to that binary's own license.

This project also integrates with, but does not redistribute, the Sanaei `3x-ui`
panel (https://github.com/MHSanaei/3x-ui), which is released under its own
license. Communication with `3x-ui` happens exclusively over its public HTTP
API on the user's own server.
